snacks.title: Protein Donut – Chocolate
snacks.body:
Who doesn’t love donuts? They’re sweet and delicious, and they’re one of America’s favorite indulgences. But are donuts really all that bad for you?
            Well, it depends. If you’re eating a donut that’s loaded with sugar and unhealthy fats, then yes, it’s probably not doing your body any favors. But if you’re enjoying a high protein donut like this that’s made with healthy ingredients and isn’t overly sweet, then it can actually be a reasonably nutritious snack!

pasta.title: Proti High Protein Orzo
pasta.body: With Proti high protein Orzo pasta, you can finally enjoy pasta again and maintain your low carb diet. Gluten-free and sugar-free, this orzo is loaded with 18 grams of protein and yet it has only 4 net carbs per serving! The options are endless…add pasta sauce for a tasty hot meal or mix with vegetables and a light olive oil for a cold pasta salad. Seven servings per box.

pasta.title: Alfredo Chicken Pasta
pasta.body: Chicken Alfredo is typically a no-no while you are losing weight. An typical dish can have more than 900 calories, loads of fat, and an entire day of carbs. However, we’ve made a version suited for a weight loss diet. Now you can enjoy alfredo pasta with just 15 grams of carbs, and only 130 calories.

pasta.title: High Protein Creamy Chicken Pasta
pasta.body: Our light creamy chicken pasta has a comfortingly creamy and cheesy sauce with a scrumptious chicken flavor that you’ll love. Not only is this a delicious meal, but it is packed with 15g of protein to help you build lean, healthy muscle. Seven single-serving packets per box.

pasta.title: Proti-Thin High Protein Fusilli
pasta.body: The Proti-Thin Fusilli Protein Pasta is an unbelievably tasty pasta that includes an astounding 18 grams of protein in every serving and is an excellent source of iron. Not only is this high protein pasta low carb, it is also low on the Glycemic Index, which makes it the perfect choice for individuals struggling with diabetes. Proti products have proved popular with our customers because they taste great, use healthy ingredients, and provide an easy solution to hard to find products like low carb pasta. Seven servings per box.

baverage.body: Building your body with the right ingredients, this thick chocolate protein shake will ensure you get ample protein every day. This delicious and easily manageable shake is portable and will easily fit into your daily work regimen or workout timetable when you need a power-up. 15 grams of protein per serving.

baverage.title: High Protein Orange Shot

This orange, single shot protein drink will help you give your body what it craves, whether you’re at work, home, or somewhere in between. Refreshing, healthy, and light, our whey protein shot offers 15 grams of protein, without all the calories. Stock up today and see the difference it makes in how you look and feel.

It comes in a ready to drink, easy to carry bottle you can drink on the go. No sugar. No fat. Just pure protein!
